<item>
            <title>[BATCH-765] StepExecution should be saved on every commit</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-765</link>
                <project id="10090" key="BATCH">Spring Batch</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;StepExecution is saved when step starts and updated when step ends, but it is not being updated after chunk is commited. This means the statistics such as item_count are reflected in the database only once the step has finished executing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
